.container

	%h1 Use the pomegranate-cli gem to create tutorial steps out of your commits. Then come back here.

	%p First install the gem:

	%code gem install pomegranate-cli

	%p Then in the root directory of your repo, type:
	
	%span 
		%code pomegranate init

	%p Then, in order, choose which files and commits you would like to be your tutorial steps. For each step, give an instruction to your students.

	%p Once your file has been written, push to Github and refresh this page.